00:31:39,063 --> 00:31:41,316
I've already told you this before.

277
00:31:41,816 --> 00:31:44,110
We've done so many exams.

278
00:31:44,193 --> 00:31:46,070
Everything is normal with your eyes.

279
00:31:46,946 --> 00:31:50,033
None of the exams
showed any abnormalities.

280
00:31:51,784 --> 00:31:52,827
Have you considered

281
00:31:53,328 --> 00:31:55,121
that your inability to see

282
00:31:55,204 --> 00:31:57,040
wasn't caused by your eyes?

283
00:31:57,540 --> 00:32:00,627
I suggest you go to
the neurology department for a brain scan.

284
00:32:00,710 --> 00:32:02,420
You may even want

285
00:32:03,254 --> 00:32:05,924
to consider a consultation
with a psychiatrist.

286
00:32:37,997 --> 00:32:41,626
FATHER: CHIANG CHIH-CHENG
MOTHER: CHOU MEI-YUN

287
00:32:41,709 --> 00:32:43,044
<i>Whose names are these?</i>

288
00:32:44,295 --> 00:32:46,130
<i>Aren't my parents called…</i>

289
00:32:50,385 --> 00:32:52,553
<i>Why can't I remember their names?</i>

290
00:32:53,972 --> 00:32:55,306
<i>What are their names?</i>

291
00:32:56,265 --> 00:32:58,184
<i>Why can't I remember?</i>

292
00:33:01,396 --> 00:33:03,982
<i>Why did I think they were dead?</i>

293
00:33:04,732 --> 00:33:05,733
<i>They…</i>

294
00:33:06,943 --> 00:33:08,444
<i>Are they really dead?</i>

295
00:33:13,616 --> 00:33:15,076
<i>In other news,</i>

296
00:33:15,159 --> 00:33:19,747
<i>on the morning of the 12th, a body</i>
<i>was found floating near a fishing port.</i>

297
00:33:19,831 --> 00:33:21,749
<i>The police, firefighters, and coast guard</i>

298
00:33:21,833 --> 00:33:24,293
<i>responded to the report</i>
<i>and recovered the body.</i>

299
00:33:24,377 --> 00:33:28,131
<i>The condition of the body suggests</i>
<i>that the man suffered severe head trauma.</i>

300
00:33:28,214 --> 00:33:30,717
<i>There was no identification,</i>

301
00:33:30,800 --> 00:33:34,095
<i>and the body was unrecognizable,</i>
<i>having been in water for days.</i>

302
00:33:34,178 --> 00:33:35,930
<i>Dental impressions and DNA analysis</i>

303
00:33:36,014 --> 00:33:38,224
<i>revealed the deceased man's</i>
<i>surname as Fan.</i>

304
00:33:38,307 --> 00:33:39,726
<i>He was allegedly linked to gangs.</i>

305
00:33:39,809 --> 00:33:42,061
<i>The police are now investigating</i>

306
00:33:42,145 --> 00:33:45,898
<i>whether the case was motivated</i>
<i>by a romantic dispute or a gang feud.</i>

307
00:33:59,078 --> 00:34:00,204
<i>That day,</i>

308
00:34:01,039 --> 00:34:03,124
<i>those boys weren't the only ones there.</i>

309
00:34:04,250 --> 00:34:05,710
<i>Chang En-ya was there too.</i>

310
00:34:06,711 --> 00:34:09,464
And it seemed like
she already knew what would happen.

311
00:34:09,964 --> 00:34:12,258
When those boys threw
Hsiao-tung onto the table,

312
00:34:12,341 --> 00:34:14,093
she immediately dragged me away.

313
00:34:15,261 --> 00:34:17,764
I had no idea that
this would happen beforehand.

314
00:34:18,389 --> 00:34:21,434
I wanted to call the police,
but Chang En-ya threatened me.

315
00:34:21,517 --> 00:34:24,937
She said that if I told anyone,
they would do the same thing to me.

316
00:34:26,272 --> 00:34:29,484
She even warned me
not to testify against them.

317
00:34:29,567 --> 00:34:31,611
So you just left Hsiao-tung there?

318
00:34:32,278 --> 00:34:34,030
I was just a high schooler.

319
00:34:34,781 --> 00:34:36,032
I was innocent.

320
00:34:36,115 --> 00:34:38,201
I didn't do anything wrong. It was them.

321
00:34:38,284 --> 00:34:41,788
Are you sure you really were innocent?

322
00:34:43,414 --> 00:34:46,918
Later on, when the school
asked you what had happened,

323
00:34:47,001 --> 00:34:48,711
you know very well

324
00:34:49,587 --> 00:34:51,214
what you told them.

325
00:34:57,470 --> 00:34:59,597
Not only did you do nothing
to save Hsiao-tung,

326
00:35:00,098 --> 00:35:02,058
but you also kicked her when she was down.

327
00:35:02,767 --> 00:35:05,436
-How dare you say you were innocent!
-It wasn't like that.

328
00:35:08,022 --> 00:35:09,273
I won't let this go.

329
00:35:10,441 --> 00:35:11,526
You will all pay

330
00:35:12,485 --> 00:35:14,112
for what you did to Hsiao-tung.

331
00:35:24,539 --> 00:35:25,915
