332
00:35:29,627 --> 00:35:32,380
<i>Hello, thank you</i>
<i>for your sincere invitation.</i>

333
00:35:32,463 --> 00:35:34,298
<i>En-ya is currently in Japan.</i>

334
00:35:34,382 --> 00:35:37,677
<i>We have informed her</i>
<i>of your invitation and plan.</i>

335
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:41,222
<i>We need to wait for her to return</i>
<i>before discussing this further with you.</i>

336
00:35:42,473 --> 00:35:45,268
SHEN MU TO LISA MIMI
THANK YOU, I LOOK FORWARD TO YOUR REPLY

