00:36:10,376 --> 00:36:11,419
Tien-ching?

338
00:36:32,398 --> 00:36:33,524
Don't turn on the light.

339
00:36:39,947 --> 00:36:41,157
What's the matter?

340
00:36:44,202 --> 00:36:45,411
What happened?

341
00:36:53,169 --> 00:36:54,295
Tell me.

342
00:36:57,256 --> 00:36:58,549
At least you're real, yeah?

