352
00:37:56,857 --> 00:37:57,900
I'm here again.

353
00:37:58,776 --> 00:38:00,194
What will you have today?

354
00:38:03,030 --> 00:38:04,407
The usual.

355
00:38:06,575 --> 00:38:07,952
No one's come in yet today?

356
00:38:08,035 --> 00:38:10,454
-Yeah.
-So I have the place to myself?

357
00:38:10,538 --> 00:38:11,747
Of course. Pick a seat.

358
00:38:13,624 --> 00:38:16,377
Then I'll take the one closest to you.

359
00:38:20,131 --> 00:38:22,300
It's been ages. Will you drink with me?

360
00:38:23,301 --> 00:38:24,302
I sell drinks.

361
00:38:24,385 --> 00:38:26,178
I don't drink with customers.

362
00:38:37,565 --> 00:38:40,735
I owe you and Yu an apology.

363
00:38:41,402 --> 00:38:44,447
You introduced Yu to me,
but I haven't done her any favors.

364
00:38:45,406 --> 00:38:49,785
I even let that jerk, Hsu Ta-wei,
order her around like she's a maid.

365
00:38:50,286 --> 00:38:51,620
I'm fine.

366
00:38:53,331 --> 00:38:54,582
Ta-wei is fun.

367
00:38:55,082 --> 00:38:56,417
How?

368
00:38:56,500 --> 00:39:00,212
He's a damn stubborn mama's boy.

369
00:39:01,881 --> 00:39:04,050
Whenever I ask him
to decline unprofitable jobs,

370
00:39:04,633 --> 00:39:05,676
he just ignores me.

371
00:39:06,177 --> 00:39:09,430
Does he even know how tiring it is
to sustain the company all by myself?

372
00:39:10,014 --> 00:39:11,807
He has never thought about you

373
00:39:11,891 --> 00:39:13,017
or me.

374
00:39:13,601 --> 00:39:15,144
He only thinks about himself.

375
00:39:15,227 --> 00:39:16,228
Hey.

376
00:39:17,605 --> 00:39:18,689
I want a drink too.

377
00:39:19,982 --> 00:39:20,858
Make it sweet.

378
00:39:21,442 --> 00:39:23,069
Isn't it better not to drink?

379
00:39:27,073 --> 00:39:29,617
Just give me a tiny bit.

380
00:39:30,493 --> 00:39:31,660
It's all your fault.

381
00:39:33,537 --> 00:39:35,039
Good thing you're not married.

382
00:39:55,810 --> 00:39:56,977
Remember.

383
00:39:58,187 --> 00:40:00,564
For our good friend's sake…

384
00:40:02,650 --> 00:40:04,860
you have to keep this secret.

385
00:41:09,508 --> 00:41:11,385
What happened?

386
00:41:18,559 --> 00:41:19,810
What is this?

387
00:41:19,894 --> 00:41:21,687
What happened?

388
00:41:30,279 --> 00:41:32,114
I went to see Shen Mu yesterday.

389
00:41:32,615 --> 00:41:33,866
Then what?

390
00:41:36,035 --> 00:41:36,869
I'll just ask her.

391
00:41:38,913 --> 00:41:40,372
The 17th?

392
00:41:40,456 --> 00:41:42,666
Yesterday was only the 5th.
How is it the 17th?

393
00:41:43,167 --> 00:41:44,585
Is this broken?

394
00:41:45,085 --> 00:41:46,170
APRIL 17TH, MONDAY

395
00:41:46,253 --> 00:41:48,589
It really is the 17th? What's going on?

396
00:41:48,672 --> 00:41:49,757
TA-WEI

397
00:41:49,840 --> 00:41:51,383
<i>-Chou Pin-yu!</i>
-Hi, Ta-wei.

398
00:41:51,467 --> 00:41:54,136
<i>Don't fucking tell me</i>
<i>that you're still sleeping.</i>

399
00:41:55,471 --> 00:41:57,598
No, I'm already on my way.

400
00:41:57,681 --> 00:41:58,807
<i>You're still on the way?</i>

401
00:41:58,891 --> 00:42:00,184
<i>What? Still on the way?</i>

402
00:42:00,768 --> 00:42:02,686
Ta-wei, I'm sorry.

403
00:42:03,187 --> 00:42:05,898
Could you first tell me
what we're doing today?

404
00:42:06,482 --> 00:42:08,943
<i>Didn't I tell you yesterday</i>
<i>we're meeting an investor?</i>

405
00:42:09,026 --> 00:42:10,903
<i>You even set the time and place yourself.</i>

406
00:42:10,986 --> 00:42:12,780
<i>What's going on with you, Chou Pin-yu?</i>

407
00:42:17,493 --> 00:42:19,453
I told you. We should've taken the stairs…

408
00:42:19,537 --> 00:42:23,374
<i>Sis, I don't remember anything</i>
<i>after I visited you that day.</i>

409
00:42:23,457 --> 00:42:26,085
<i>Suddenly, a few days have passed.</i>
<i>What exactly happened?</i>

410
00:42:26,627 --> 00:42:28,212
<i>Did you take me home that day?</i>

411
00:42:28,712 --> 00:42:30,673
<i>Did I say anything to you afterward?</i>

412
00:42:32,132 --> 00:42:35,261
<i>Can I come over after work?</i>
<i>I need to talk to you about something.</i>

413
00:42:36,262 --> 00:42:37,096
Chou Pin-yu.

414
00:42:37,638 --> 00:42:40,349
How many times have I told you?
Don't text and chat at work.

415
00:42:40,432 --> 00:42:41,600
Sorry.

416
00:42:42,226 --> 00:42:43,519
Which number is it?

417
00:43:06,083 --> 00:43:06,917
Tien-ching?

418
00:43:23,267 --> 00:43:24,935
What a coincidence.

419
00:43:25,019 --> 00:43:26,061
Why are you here?

420
00:43:26,145 --> 00:43:27,688
It's been so long.

421
00:43:27,771 --> 00:43:28,981
How have you been?

422
00:43:29,607 --> 00:43:30,941
Are you here to see a doctor?

423
00:43:42,286 --> 00:43:43,495
We're here for work.

424
00:43:44,580 --> 00:43:46,165
I'm her boss. Hello.

425
00:43:46,248 --> 00:43:47,333
Hello.

426
00:43:49,501 --> 00:43:51,128
You haven't forgotten me, have you?

427
00:43:52,004 --> 00:43:53,047
I'm Joy.

428
00:43:54,840 --> 00:43:56,383
Hey, Yu.

429
00:43:56,884 --> 00:43:58,135
What's that look for?

430
00:43:59,178 --> 00:44:00,304
What's wrong?

431
00:44:01,013 --> 00:44:03,432
You know, you did me
a huge favor back then.

432
00:44:03,515 --> 00:44:05,184
I've always wanted to thank you.

433
00:44:07,686 --> 00:44:09,146
-I've been meaning to.
-Yu?

434
00:44:09,229 --> 00:44:10,397
-Back at the radio…
-Yu?

435
00:44:10,981 --> 00:44:12,441
Lucky you were there for me.

436
00:44:12,524 --> 00:44:14,777
So everything went well
for me and my wife.

437
00:44:15,402 --> 00:44:16,612
Tien-ching?

438
00:44:17,237 --> 00:44:19,406
-Yu?
-Are you okay?

439
00:44:19,490 --> 00:44:20,616
Yu?

440
00:44:20,699 --> 00:44:21,825
Hey, you're scaring me.

441
00:44:22,910 --> 00:44:24,119
Yu.

